ch is good ‘cause I’m still editing for crying out loud!) but acceptance wasn’t the aim. I heard those shitty lies, accepted my fear, and actively chose to me courageous. Fuck you, depression!

Front Page Edit:
I guess I should do this? I didn't think this would get any traction at all. Thank you all for the lovely words and offers for help! It means quite a lot to get kudos, validation, encouragement, and basic attention from random strangers... or something. 

